<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>손현빈</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#f6f3ec;
    --ink:#1c1a17;
    --muted:#6f685d;
    --line:#ddd6c8;
    --accent:#c2502b;
    --accent-soft:#e8d9cf;
    --serif:"Iowan Old Style","Palatino Linotype",Palatino,Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
    --sans:"Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,"Segoe UI",Roboto,sans-serif;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--sans);
    line-height:1.7;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }
  .wrap{
    max-width:680px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 28px;
  }

  /* header */
  header{
    padding:38px 0 0;
  }
  .topbar{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:baseline;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom:18px;
  }
  .mark{
    font-family:var(--serif);
    font-size:1.05rem;
    font-weight:600;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
  }
  .topbar nav a{
    color:var(--muted);
    text-decoration:none;
    font-size:0.82rem;
    margin-left:20px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:0.12em;
    transition:color .25s ease;
  }
  .topbar nav a:hover{color:var(--accent)}

  /* hero */
  .hero{
    padding:96px 0 84px;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-size:0.78rem;
    letter-spacing:0.22em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--accent);
    margin-bottom:26px;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-family:var(--serif);
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:clamp(3rem,11vw,5.4rem);
    line-height:0.98;
    letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    margin-bottom:30px;
  }
  .hero h1 .dot{color:var(--accent)}
  .hero p{
    font-size:1.18rem;
    color:var(--muted);
    max-width:30ch;
  }
  .hero p b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}

  /* sections */
  section{padding:62px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .label{
    font-size:0.76rem;
    letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
    margin-bottom:42px;
  }

  .work{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
  }
  .item{
    display:flex;
    gap:26px;
    padding:26px 6px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    align-items:baseline;
    transition:padding-left .3s ease,background .3s ease;
  }
  .item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .item:hover{
    padding-left:18px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent-soft),transparent 70%);
  }
  .num{
    font-family:var(--serif);
    font-size:0.95rem;
    color:var(--accent);
    min-width:32px;
  }
  .item h3{
    font-family:var(--serif);
    font-size:1.5rem;
    font-weight:600;
    margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .item .desc{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.98rem}

  /* contact */
  #contact .links{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:14px;
  }
  .chip{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    text-decoration:none;
    color:var(--ink);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:12px 22px;
    font-size:0.95rem;
    transition:border-color .25s ease,color .25s ease,transform .25s ease;
  }
  .chip:hover{
    border-color:var(--accent);
    color:var(--accent);
    transform:translateY(-2px);
  }
  .chip span{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.08em}

  footer{
    padding:48px 0 64px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    color:var(--muted);
    font-size:0.82rem;
  }
  footer .mark{font-size:0.92rem}

  @media (max-width:520px){
    .topbar nav a:first-child{display:none}
    .item{gap:16px}
    footer{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="topbar">
        <div class="mark">손현빈</div>
        <nav>
          <a href="#work">하는 일</a>
          <a href="#contact">연락처</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero" style="border-top:none">
        <p class="eyebrow">개발자 · 기록하는 사람</p>
        <h1>손현빈<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
        <p>만드는 걸 좋아하고, 그 과정을 <b>글로 남기는 사람</b>입니다.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="work">
        <p class="label">하는 일</p>
        <div class="work">
          <div class="item">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <div>
              <h3>개발</h3>
              <p class="desc">웹과 도구를 만듭니다. 작게 시작해 끝까지 다듬는 걸 좋아합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <div>
              <h3>사이드 프로젝트</h3>
              <p class="desc">필요해서, 혹은 궁금해서 만든 것들. 주말마다 무언가 자라납니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <div>
              <h3>글쓰기</h3>
              <p class="desc">배운 것과 헤맨 흔적을 정리해 둡니다. 다음의 나를 위한 기록.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <p class="label">연락처</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a class="chip" href="mailto:hello@hyunbin.dev">
            <span>EMAIL</span> hello@hyunbin.dev
          </a>
          <a class="chip" href="https://github.com/hyunbin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span>GITHUB</span> github.com/hyunbin
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="mark">손현빈</div>
      <div>© 2026 — 천천히, 꾸준히.</div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>